Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.87,0:00:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥殿下，冷静一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.64,0:00:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了，来了，戴芬妮来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.31,0:00:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.51,0:00:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.68,0:00:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快逃，快逃，快逃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.72,0:00:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.58,0:00:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加冕仪式会场上\N出现了基尔特战舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.95,0:00:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对方在到处洒落蔷薇花瓣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.72,0:00:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蔷薇？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.03,0:00:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轮机室，开到最大航速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.76,0:00:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全体人员进入战斗状态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.43,0:00:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把它击沈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.77,0:00:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊，舰长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.13,0:00:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下方有副舰长……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.04,0:00:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙就在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.84,0:00:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个总帅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.89,0:01:04.12,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,just keep on trying, keep on flying\N{\c&HFFBF00&}just keep on trying, keep on flying
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.19,0:01:07.78,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be the light\N{\c&HFFBF00&}I will be the light
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.86,0:01:15.06,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果说把黎明　当作是一个开始\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜明けをひと　つの始まりとするなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.13,0:01:22.06,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果说现在就是来临的时刻\N{\c&HFFBF00&}今が来るべき時だとするなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.14,0:01:26.67,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,与你的烟云时代交响曲\N{\c&HFFBF00&}君とのCloud Age Symphony
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.75,0:01:36.05,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,飞向云海的彼端　飞往光芒照射的方向\N{\c&HFFBF00&}雲の海の向こうに　光が射す方へ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.66,0:01:51.02,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah～是否可以遇见有如魔法的那一刻？\N{\c&HFFBF00&}Ah～魔法のような一瞬に会えるのか？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.10,0:01:58.31,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,取代寒冷的黑夜\N{\c&HFFBF00&}冷たい夜を引き替えに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.38,0:02:05.41,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,我俩展翅飞翔\N{\c&HFFBF00&}二人は羽ばたいて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.48,0:02:16.36,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,在那尽头  抓住了永恒…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}永远を掴む、その果てには
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.71,0:02:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H8dccf0&}西西里式防御\NSicilian Defence
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.29,0:02:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.96,0:02:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加冕仪式怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.03,0:02:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也好想看看\N副舰长盛装的样子说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.37,0:02:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家可是苏菲亚皇帝呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.44,0:03:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们船上\N可是坐过个了不得的人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.28,0:03:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那还用说，副舰长可不是盖的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.44,0:03:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇，是花瓣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.35,0:03:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基尔特为什么要\N那么大张旗鼓的来祝贺啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.45,0:03:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.75,0:03:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整个天空都被染红了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.82,0:03:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是好漂亮呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.53,0:03:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.23,0:03:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还剩六天……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.05,0:03:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请问舰长什么时候才会回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.72,0:03:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.19,0:03:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他只是和基尔特那位大姐\N曾经有些过节罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.39,0:03:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大姐？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.39,0:03:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事啦，你别在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.66,0:03:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距离龙之牙还有800
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.70,0:03:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接近岩礁中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.53,0:03:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仰角15度，把高度拉高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.00,0:03:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.13,0:04:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仔细收听周围的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.54,0:04:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.65,0:04:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到有动力音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.62,0:04:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对照音纹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.42,0:04:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下方发现了\N无音航行中的乌尔班号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.72,0:04:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.46,0:04:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这时候碰到乌尔班号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.33,0:04:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是来报仇的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.86,0:04:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次非得搞定它不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.50,0:04:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全舰进入战斗位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.60,0:04:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面有皇帝的旗帜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.51,0:04:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对方发出了停战信号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.94,0:04:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.61,0:04:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乌尔班号要求准许接舷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.93,0:05:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戴芬妮总帅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.24,0:05:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她还真是打了个大招呼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.78,0:05:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正在让脑袋冷静下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.62,0:05:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉，东西丢得到处都是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.12,0:05:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是想让我击沈你吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.73,0:05:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,皇帝……陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.07,0:05:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照以往那样\N叫我苏菲亚就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.58,0:05:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.61,0:05:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想应该在停机库吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.38,0:05:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.06,0:06:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副舰长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.29,0:06:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是大风暴区的航路图\N对不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.70,0:06:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，这是由度西斯所提供的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.27,0:06:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.57,0:06:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十年前\N你目击到EXILE的地点在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.35,0:06:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.42,0:06:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,组件没有遭到基尔特的控制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.06,0:06:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有办法冲进大风暴区的船舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.76,0:06:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在也只有\N银之战舰和乌尔班号了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.77,0:06:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以靠这两艘来找到EXILE……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.93,0:06:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要靠银之战舰就绰绰有余了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.24,0:06:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是军令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.14,0:06:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没有拒绝的权利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.88,0:07:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抢夺组件行动预定在\N山羊月13日04：00时进行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.38,0:07:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前我们必须找到EXILE\N并且抓到它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.39,0:07:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有……六天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.39,0:07:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在冲进大风暴区之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.36,0:07:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由乌尔班号发射音响鱼雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.80,0:07:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后靠它的搜索音来找出EXILE
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.77,0:07:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是光靠搜索音来确认目标\N恐怕……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.64,0:07:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以说我才准备了这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.94,0:07:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葳娜\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.24,0:07:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是度西斯所捕捉到的\NEXILE的驱动音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.75,0:07:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葳娜，你应该办得到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.62,0:07:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.62,0:07:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会留在银之战舰上担任指挥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.33,0:07:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下\N怎么可以让这种破船……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.20,0:07:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.20,0:07:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说怎么可以\N把陛下留在这艘船上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.70,0:07:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你别担心我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.71,0:08:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我对这里很熟悉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.78,0:08:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我那不妙的预感果然应验了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.65,0:08:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把皇帝旗降下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.26,0:08:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还挺周到的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.79,0:08:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝大风暴区出发啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.70,0:08:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，两位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.14,0:08:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要用用看这架子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.14,0:08:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很结实唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.74,0:08:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇，好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.37,0:08:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那种比赛用的机型\N恐怕抵不住强风吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.25,0:08:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.45,0:08:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢……谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.88,0:08:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.29,0:08:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副舰长……副舰长她回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.12,0:08:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不是已经是皇帝了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.53,0:08:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全体船员请注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.13,0:09:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本舰从现在起将和乌尔班号\N一起朝大风暴区出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.67,0:09:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大风暴区
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.34,0:09:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是副舰长的声音耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.18,0:09:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本次作战将与麦德赛舰队\N以及度西斯残存舰队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.65,0:09:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所组成的同盟舰队\N采取一致步调
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.32,0:09:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来迫使基尔特公会的\N戴芬妮总帅投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.42,0:09:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们将作为主力军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.39,0:09:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在六天后的山羊月13日04：00前\N找到位于大风暴区中的EXILE
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.63,0:09:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么是EXILE
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.11,0:09:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不要担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.65,0:09:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去问问看苏菲亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.38,0:09:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.12,0:09:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.18,0:09:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.65,0:09:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了在大风暴区里\N进行声纳搜索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.12,0:10:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在下令无音航行后\N请全舰彻底保持肃静
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.43,0:10:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次作战是否能够成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.76,0:10:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,端看全体船员的努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.10,0:10:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副舰长……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.57,0:10:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这下薪水有着落了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.17,0:10:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在此期许各位都能全力以赴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.65,0:10:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全体人员进入战斗位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.05,0:10:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始朝大风暴区前进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.73,0:10:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.20,0:10:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起舰桥工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.27,0:10:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果你还是选择了\N驾驶员这条路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.47,0:10:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.71,0:10:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想成为\N像克劳士那样的驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.68,0:10:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.25,0:10:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苏菲亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.46,0:11:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苏菲亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.14,0:11:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.54,0:11:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有获准求见吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.27,0:11:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有事要说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.21,0:11:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我退下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.78,0:11:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.45,0:11:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你进来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.82,0:11:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苏菲亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.42,0:11:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾儿她到底会怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.99,0:11:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾儿她和EXILE\N到底有着什么关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.06,0:11:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾儿她……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.80,0:11:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你坐下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.37,0:11:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾儿．薇丝是启动EXILE\N所不可或缺的一把钥匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.11,0:11:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕是成功抢夺了组件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.38,0:12:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要对抗基尔特公会\N还是需要EXILE
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.95,0:12:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EXILE是带领我们安那托勒\N与度西斯走向和平的最后希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.89,0:12:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对你而言\N艾儿终究也只是个货物吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.30,0:12:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.53,0:12:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会保护艾儿．薇丝的安全的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.84,0:12:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.98,0:12:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.65,0:12:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎你回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.20,0:12:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.20,0:12:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士在吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.77,0:12:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，迪奥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.94,0:12:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨……嗨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.91,0:13:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.71,0:13:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.58,0:13:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看，很漂亮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.88,0:13:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些花瓣完全不会枯萎耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.37,0:13:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.40,0:13:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.40,0:13:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯是什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.81,0:13:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了对抗基尔特公会\NEXILE是必须的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.38,0:13:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.31,0:13:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是苏菲亚跟你这么说的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.71,0:13:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那，艾儿呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.38,0:13:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她叫我不用担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.48,0:13:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就这样相信了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.75,0:13:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有够烂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.85,0:13:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是，我会保护艾儿的\N所以不用担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.42,0:13:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.63,0:13:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾儿呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.20,0:13:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.27,0:14:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.57,0:14:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.41,0:14:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家好心拿花给他看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.98,0:14:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥他却……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.18,0:14:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.52,0:14:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥他……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.45,0:14:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.65,0:14:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾儿，打起精神来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.69,0:14:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾儿你喜欢虫子吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.53,0:14:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虫子？我讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.40,0:14:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.83,0:14:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.60,0:14:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我就不怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.27,0:14:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许有人就是讨厌花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.04,0:14:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.87,0:14:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,……生日周？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.81,0:14:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，听说基尔特的人\N都会庆祝一个礼拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.68,0:14:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是生日应该是一件\N值得高兴的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.02,0:14:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果没有人帮忙庆祝\N是很寂寞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.92,0:14:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说得有道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.27,0:15:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钢缆不够长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.63,0:15:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，莫蓝你拿钢缆给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.80,0:15:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.47,0:15:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫蓝走了以后\N你好像满寂寞的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.04,0:15:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.34,0:15:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他如果继续待在这里的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.48,0:15:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该可以成为一个\N技术高超的维修士的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.81,0:15:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他已经找到自己要走的路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.55,0:15:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么办法呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.99,0:15:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没找到迪奥吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.56,0:15:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十分抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.60,0:15:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无能可是一种罪哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.40,0:15:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是在干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.64,0:15:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来是在把水运往干旱的地带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.11,0:15:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真难看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.88,0:15:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把它的组件收回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.25,0:15:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是他们并没有违反任何规则
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.52,0:15:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,属下遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.85,0:15:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就照您的意思去办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.46,0:16:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,度西斯的船\N马上就会把水运过来了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.90,0:16:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,荷莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.64,0:16:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这就要走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.54,0:16:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.14,0:16:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次什么时候回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.41,0:16:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很快就会有一场大战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.42,0:16:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.12,0:16:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是那位总帅\N给同盟的回答吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.06,0:16:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一切结束后\N我立刻就会来接你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.66,0:16:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您要保重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.40,0:16:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.53,0:17:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.84,0:17:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,借我看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.24,0:17:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.84,0:17:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是度西斯的最新型吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.74,0:17:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里栓得太紧了一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.31,0:17:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样会比较好用哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.72,0:17:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.29,0:17:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你胸口那个是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.63,0:17:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.46,0:17:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我活着回来的证明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.00,0:17:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,数目好多哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.23,0:17:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我劝你最好不要离开我身边哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.31,0:18:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来我又提前出局了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.71,0:18:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟拉薇，还有塔琪安娜的时候\N也都是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.91,0:18:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真丢脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.78,0:18:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会这么做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.72,0:18:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么又是鸟肉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.45,0:18:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.72,0:18:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是鸟蛋你都吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.52,0:18:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸟蛋和鸟不一样好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.03,0:18:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不吃鸟肉的话\N当心没有体力哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.37,0:18:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是克劳士\N也能和我们一起飞就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.55,0:18:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子乘着银之战舰\N飞到很高的地方去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.75,0:18:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么跩哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.15,0:18:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不晓得他是去干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.19,0:18:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是去杀无赦去了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.09,0:18:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们都进步很快嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.53,0:18:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别忘了我可是拿到\N诺齐亚杯冠军的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.40,0:19:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我住嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.70,0:19:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只是狗屎运捞到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.70,0:19:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.90,0:19:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正式行动时也拜托你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.75,0:19:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是宣誓的印记吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.22,0:19:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到时候你将会失去\N飞翔在天空的自由与快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.09,0:19:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样你也无所谓吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.23,0:19:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么所谓无所谓的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.93,0:19:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然这是戴芬妮决定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.70,0:19:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也只有这样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.40,0:19:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉……真是令人讨厌的仪式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.77,0:19:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想永远都待在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.22,0:19:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,砂糖好像加得太多了点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.82,0:19:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.65,0:19:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样做出来才好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.62,0:19:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是……是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.23,0:20:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越来越接近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.10,0:20:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.90,0:20:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们去看看好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.33,0:20:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到外头去看大风暴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.67,0:20:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是度西斯船舰残骸的反射音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.78,0:20:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是雨候鸟拍翅的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.02,0:20:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最初的第一发……在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.62,0:20:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.39,0:20:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于要冲入大风暴区了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.09,0:20:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距离捕获EXILE的最后期限\N还剩五天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.36,0:20:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发射鱼雷的这一方\N责任也相当重大呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.77,0:20:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音响鱼雷，准备发射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.24,0:20:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乌尔班号来电
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.64,0:20:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鱼雷发射已准备就绪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.45,0:20:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可别走得太远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.52,0:21:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好冷……好冰的风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.66,0:21:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.04,0:21:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要进去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.28,0:21:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进入大风暴区
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.94,0:21:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作好冲击防备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.88,0:21:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全舰准备进行无音航行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.19,0:21:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关闭所有隔舱，停止空调
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.66,0:21:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会不会还是\N不要用堆起来的比较好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.03,0:21:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保……保持安静
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.24,0:21:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听音准备就绪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.51,0:22:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，发射音响鱼雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.42,0:22:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是\N吞噬了爸爸他们的大风暴区……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.38,0:22:39.54,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,黑夜的时光逐渐逼近\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜の時間が迫り来る
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.15,0:22:46.21,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你离我如此接近感觉  却好远…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたはこんな近く  でも遠い…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.29,0:22:57.36,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你的憧憬是什么  心中想的又是誰\N{\c&HFFBF00&}何に憧れて だれを想うのか
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.43,0:23:02.96,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你舍命奋斗的身影\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いのち賭ける姿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.04,0:23:11.74,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,有一种透明的美丽  令我不禁哑口无言\N{\c&HFFBF00&}透き通る美しさに 言葉を飲んだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.82,0:23:17.69,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你欲飞往天际\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたが空を行くなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.75,0:23:23.49,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,我愿成为你的翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}わたしは翼になりたい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.56,0:23:29.36,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,无论风有多么强\N{\c&HFFBF00&}どんなに強い風にも
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.43,0:23:35.13,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,也永远不会折断的柔婉翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}けして折れない しなやかな羽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.21,0:23:47.17,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,相信有一天  我会拥有那样一对翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いつか　きっと持つから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.76,0:23:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（下回预告）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.89,0:23:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是度西斯船舰残骸的反射音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.73,0:23:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是雨候鸟拍翅的声音
